      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·邶風·016.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">北風.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>北風其涼，雨雪其雱，
惠而好我，攜手同行，【韻：雱行】
其虛其邪，既亟只且。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Cold blows the north wind;
Thick falls the snow.
Ye who love and regard me,
Let us join hands and go together.
Is it a time for delay?
The urgency is extreme!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-beifeng-016__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
