      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·邶風·016.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">北風.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>莫赤匪狐，莫黑匪烏，
惠而好我，攜手同車，【韻：烏車】
其虛其邪，既亟只且。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Nothing red is seen but foxes,
Nothing black but crows.
Ye who love and regard me,
Let us join hands, and go together in our carriages.
Is it a time for delay?
The urgency is extreme!</seg>
      </tuv>
